01308 Premiership Rugby|2007\u201308]]\n|-\n|align=center | 4\n|[[Saracens F.C.|Saracens]]\n| align=center | 5\n|[[2010\u201311 Premiership Rugby|2010\u201311]], [[2014\u201315 Premiership Rugby|2014\u201315]], [[2015\u201316 Premiership Rugby|2015\u201316]], [[2017\u201318 Premiership Rugby|2017\u201318]], [[2018\u201319 Premiership Rugby|2018\u201319]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" align=center | 5\n|[[Newcastle Falcons]]\n| rowspan=\"5\"; align=center | 1\n|[[1997\u201398 Premiership Rugby|1997\u201398]]\n|-\n|[[Sale Sharks]]\n|[[2005\u201306 Premiership Rugby|2005\u201306]]\n|-\n|[[Harlequin F.C.|Harlequins]]\n|[[2011\u201312 Premiership Rugby|2011\u201312]]\n|-\n|[[Northampton Saints]]\n|[[2013\u201314 Premiership Rugby|2013\u201314]]\n|-\n|[[Exeter Chiefs]]\n|[[2016\u201317 Premiership Rugby|2016\u201317]]\n|}\n\n<br />\n\n== Attendances ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Season\n!Total\n!width|Average\n|-\n|[[2002\u201303 Premiership Rugby|2002\u201303]]\n|1,183,972\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|8,518\n|-\n|[[2003\u201304 Premiership Rugby|2003\u201304]]\n|1,241,557\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|9,062\n|-\n|[[2004\u201305 Premiership Rugby|2004\u201305]]\n|1,481,355\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|10,813\n|-\n|[[2005\u201306 Premiership Rugby|2005\u201306]]\n|1,483,920\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|10,922\n|-\n|[[2006\u201307 Premiership Rugby|2006\u201307]]\n|1,598,734\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|11,842\n|-\n|[[2007\u201308 Premiership Rugby|2007\u201308]]\n|1,517,863\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|11,243\n|-\n|[[2008\u201309 Premiership Rugby|2008\u201309]]\n|1,671,781\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|12,384\n|-\n|[[2009\u201310 Premiership Rugby|2009\u201310]]\n|1,900,177\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|14,075\n|-\n|[[2010\u201311 Premiership Rugby|2010\u201311]]\n|1,740,751\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|12,894\n|-\n|[[2011\u201312 Premiership Rugby|2011\u201312]]\n|1,755,073\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|13,001\n|-\n|[[2012\u201313 Premiership Rugby|2012\u